@startuml
title UC-03 - Sequencia Enviar Presente Digital
autonumber

actor Parceiro
participant "App Mobile" as Mobile
participant "API NestJS" as API
participant "GiftService" as GiftService
participant "PaymentAdapter" as PaymentAdapter
participant "Gateway de Pagamento" as Payment
participant "NotificationService" as Notification
participant "CanalNotificacaoStrategy" as Strategy
database "PostgreSQL" as DB

Parceiro -> Mobile: selecionar gift card
Mobile -> API: POST /gifts
API -> GiftService: enviarPresente(dto)
GiftService -> PaymentAdapter: processarPagamento()\n<<Adapter>>
PaymentAdapter -> Payment: criar transacao
Payment --> PaymentAdapter: pagamento aprovado
GiftService -> DB: salvar presente e status
GiftService -> Notification: enviarSurpresa(casal)
Notification -> Strategy: escolherCanal(push|in-app)\n<<Strategy>>
Strategy --> Notification: canal escolhido
API --> Mobile: 201 + presente enviado

note right of GiftService
Contrato de Operacao (CO-03)
Pre: usuario autenticado e metodo de pagamento valido.
Pos: presente persistido e parceiro notificado.
end note
@enduml

